        "\n",
        "## Overview\n",
        "\n",
        "MindBoost is a mental wellbeing app developed as part of the New Enterprise \n",
        "Development module at Dublin City University. As **CEO** of the project, \n",
        "I led a team of five students to design, research and pitch a digital \n",
        "solution for young adults struggling with stress and anxiety.\n",
        "\n",
        "## The Problem\n",
        "\n",
        "Young people aged 18-30 face increasing levels of stress and anxiety, \n",
        "yet existing mental health solutions are often too clinical, expensive \n",
        "or time-consuming for daily use.\n",
        "\n",
        "## Our Solution\n",
        "\n",
        "MindBoost offers personalised daily mental wellbeing support through:\n",
        "\n",
        "- 🧠 **AI-personalised tips** based on mood tracking\n",
        "- 📓 **Daily check-ins** with journaling and breathing exercises\n",
        "- 🎯 **Short activities** that fit into a 5-minute daily routine\n",
        "- 👨‍⚕️ **Direct therapist access** for professional support\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "## Key Research Insights\n",
        "\n",
        "| Insight | Result |\n",
        "|---------|--------|\n",
        "| Users find daily check-ins highly useful | 67.8% |\n",
        "| Appreciate direct therapist access | 67.6% |\n",
        "| Willing to pay €4.99+ per month | 35% |\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "## My Role\n",
        "\n",
        "As CEO, I was responsible for overall strategy, team coordination and \n",
        "the final pitch presentation at DCU Business School.\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "::: {.callout-note}\n",
        "This project was developed as part of the New Enterprise Development Programme at DCU Business School.\n",
        ":::\n",
        "\n",
        "## Data Analysis"
      ],
